{"title":"hexo+github搭建线上blog(基本部分)","date":"2016-10-25T06:52:39.000Z","slug":"hexo-1","tags":["hexo","tool"],"updated":"2018-10-25T07:31:59.570Z","content":"<h2 id=\"安装hexo\"><a href=\"#安装hexo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装hexo\"></a>安装hexo</h2><figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm i -g hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>判断hexo 是否安装成功<br><figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h2 id=\"初始化hexo项目\"><a href=\"#初始化hexo项目\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"初始化hexo项目\"></a>初始化hexo项目</h2><figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>成功后安装依赖<br><figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm i</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h2 id=\"构建\"><a href=\"#构建\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"构建\"></a>构建</h2><figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>\b根据<code>/source</code>路径下的文件，生成<code>/public</code>下的最终文件（也就是将要部署在github上的部分）</p>\n<h2 id=\"部署-deploy\"><a href=\"#部署-deploy\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"部署 deploy\"></a>部署 deploy</h2><p>打开配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>，\b改写以下\b配置<br><figure class=\"highlight yml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">deploy:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"attr\">type:</span> <span class=\"string\">git</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"attr\">repo:</span> <span class=\"string\">&lt;git</span> <span class=\"string\">repo</span> <span class=\"string\">url&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"attr\">branch:</span> <span class=\"string\">&lt;branch</span> <span class=\"string\">name,</span> <span class=\"string\">master</span> <span class=\"string\">default&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>这一步的目的是为了\b关联到你的github repo。此时你还没有对应的repo，在下一步创建。</p>\n<h2 id=\"创建github-repo\"><a href=\"#创建github-repo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"创建github repo\"></a>创建github repo</h2><p>将其命名为 <code>[your username].github.io</code>。然后将改仓库的地址\b写入上面的配置。这\b个行为是为了使用githug pages，和hexo无直接关系。了解<a href=\"https://pages.github.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">github pages</a>。</p>\n<h2 id=\"如何新增blog\"><a href=\"#如何新增blog\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"如何新增blog?\"></a>如何新增blog?</h2><p>使用hexo cli<br><figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"string\">\"[postName]\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>该指令将在<code>/source/_posts</code>路径下，创建一个md文件，文件名为你在上述\b指令中的填写的<code>postName</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"发布提交\"><a href=\"#发布提交\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"发布提交\"></a>发布提交</h2><figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo g -d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>该指令其实是\b\b两个指令的简写，<code>hexo g</code> 和 <code>hexo d</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"查看效果\"><a href=\"#查看效果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"查看效果\"></a>查看效果</h2><p>在浏览器访问<code>&lt;your username&gt;.github.io</code> 即可查看线上效果。</p>\n<h2 id=\"本地查看\"><a href=\"#本地查看\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"本地查看\"></a>本地查看</h2><p>如果想现在本地验看效果之后再进行提交，则可以启动本地服务<br><figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>如果一直出于启动中状态，可能是端口号被占用，可\b调整端口号<br><figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo s -p [port]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n","prev":{"title":"hexo+github搭建线上blog(主题)","slug":"hexo-3"},"next":{"title":"Hello World","slug":"hello-world"},"link":"http://qixman.github.io/post/hexo-1/","toc":[{"title":"安装hexo","id":"安装hexo","index":"1"},{"title":"初始化hexo项目","id":"初始化hexo项目","index":"2"},{"title":"构建","id":"构建","index":"3"},{"title":"部署 deploy","id":"部署-deploy","index":"4"},{"title":"创建github repo","id":"创建github-repo","index":"5"},{"title":"如何新增blog?","id":"如何新增blog","index":"6"},{"title":"发布提交","id":"发布提交","index":"7"},{"title":"查看效果","id":"查看效果","index":"8"},{"title":"本地查看","id":"本地查看","index":"9"}]}